==Introduction==
'''Mass Rapid Transit (Singapore)''' is a rail transit system in [[w:Singapore|Singapore]], with 70 stations in operation. This system is operated by the rail operator [[w:SMRT Corporation|SMRT Corporation]] and [[w:SBS Transit|SBS Transit]].

