==No order.gif files still for some kanji==
I've left a couple kanji pics without out order.gif files because apparently they still don't exist. I'm trying to learn how to create them with very little success. Any help in this area is much appreciated. On another note some of the existing order.gif files are so fuzzy they could be redone so that they meet the quality of many of the other files. Thanks [[User:Nataraja87|Nataraja87]] ([[User talk:Nataraja87|talk]]) 06:24, 17 July 2009 (UTC)

[[File:Ns5 Yew Tee.jpg|thumb|right|Yew Tee MRT Station]]

'''Yew Tee MRT Station''' is a station located on 61 [[w:Choa Chu Kang|Choa Chu Kang]] Drive, [[w:Singapore|Singapore]] 689715. It is located between [[Mass Rapid Transit (Singapore)/Choa Chu Kang MRT Station|Choa Chu Kang MRT Station]] and [[Mass Rapid Transit (Singapore)/Kranji MRT Station|Kranji MRT Station]].

